{% block projectContent %}
    <p>
        This talk was originally written specifically for the Dev Together meetup..
        If you would like me to craft a version of this presentation for your conference or event, contact me via
        <a href="mailto:j.l.unrein+contact@gmail.com">email</a> or <a
